* Testing Svelte Inlines

This is a counter component:

@inline svelte
<script>
  let count = 0;
</script>

<button on:click={() => count++}>
  Count: {count}
</button>

<style>
  button {
    background: blue;
    color: white;
  }
</style>
@end

* Multiple Inlines

First inline:

@inline svelte
<div>Hello from Svelte!</div>
@end

Second inline:

@inline svelte
<script>
  let name = "World";
</script>

<h1>Hello {name}!</h1>
@end

* Content Between Inlines

This text is between two inline blocks.

@inline svelte
<p>Another component</p>
@end

This text comes after the third inline.
